Date: 22-23 June 2020 Location: London, UK Website The Future of Mining EMEA has been created to connect C-suite, Heads and Managers ofMine Operations and Mining Equipment, Technology and Service (METS) providers from topenterprises around the globe to debate and define the future mining landscape across Europe,the Middle East and Africa. Now in its second year, the conference covers a vast range of content spanning the entire mining life cycle, focusing on the innovations and technologies driving the industry forward with senior representation from mining companies, service providers, government, finance and research organisations.